### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Signal query — RSI first slice
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Validates the signal domain vertical slice:
###   derive (RSI sampler) → SIGNAL_EVENTS → store (projection) → gateway HTTP
###
### Prerequisites:
###   make up           # starts nats, configctl, gateway, ingest, derive, store
###   make seed         # seeds configctl with btcusdt binding
###   wait ~20min       # RSI needs 15 finalized 60s candles for warm-up
###
### Note: RSI warm-up requires period+1 = 15 candles. At 60s timeframe,
### first signal appears after ~15 minutes of live data.

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### 1. Latest RSI signal — btcusdt 60s
### Expected: 200 with signal data (after warm-up) or 200 with null signal
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Latest RSI signal — btcusdt 300s
### Expected: 200 with signal data (after 15x300s = 75min warm-up) or null
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Unknown signal type — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/unknown/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Missing timeframe — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt
Accept: application/json

###

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Multi-symbol signal queries (S41 — signal multi-symbol verification)
### Prerequisites:
###   make seed-multi    (seeds configctl with btcusdt + ethusdt bindings)
###   wait ~20min        (RSI warm-up: 15 candles × 60s per candle)
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 5. Latest RSI signal — ethusdt 60s
### Expected: 200 with signal data (after warm-up) or 200 with null signal
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Latest RSI signal — ethusdt 300s
### Expected: 200 with signal data (after 15x300s = 75min warm-up) or null
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=300
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Cross-symbol verification — query btcusdt and ethusdt back-to-back
### Compare responses: symbols must differ, values should differ (different assets)
GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=btcusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/signal/rsi/latest?source=binancef&symbol=ethusdt&timeframe=60
Accept: application/json

###
